These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, ivory, red, apricot
4 different games are played: whist, go, scrabble, backgammon
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person who likes azure is the person playing whist##1
5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person playing go is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color    | ivory  | apricot | red    | azure       |
| Game         | go | backgammon    | scrabble      | whist |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, climbing, cricket, cycling
4 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit, horse, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the owner of the fish is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| Sport         | climbing | cricket | cycling | handball |
| Pet   | rabbit    | fish   | horse     | mouse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, van, tram
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, whist, snooker
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the tram is the person playing whist##1
5. the russian is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the person driving the airplane is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Transport         | airplane | motorbike | van | tram |
| Game   | snooker       | domino    | bridge | whist     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

