.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, japanese, pakistani, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, card-games, drawing, puzzles
1. the pakistani is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the japanese is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the pakistani##1
7. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the spanish is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality         | dutch | spanish | pakistani | japanese |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Hobby   | card-games | woodworking         | puzzles      | drawing        |

