.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, ivory, purple, mauve
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, september, august
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, climbing, snowboarding
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who likes blood-red is the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who likes mauve is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Color         | purple   | mauve | ivory  | blood-red      |
| Birthday   | september  | june        | august  | october       |
| Sport         | badminton | climbing    | biathlon | snowboarding |

