.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, avocado, radish, pepper
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, apricot, fuchsia, orange
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, trance
1. the person eating apple is the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
4. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
5. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes fuchsia is the person eating radish##1
7. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
8. the person eating pepper is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food           | avocado | radish | pepper | apple |
| Color   | orange   | fuchsia  | apricot | blue   |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | folk     | reggae | funk       |

