.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit, ferret, horse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, surfing, lacrosse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
8. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Pet          | cat  | horse | ferret   | rabbit     |
| Sport         | lacrosse | rowing   | snowboarding  | surfing |
| Movie-Genre   | spy         | disaster  | mystery | thriller  |

