.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
4 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, poker, domino
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, drama, mystery
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, camping, skydiving, baking
1. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is the person playing poker##1
7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
8. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Game      | domino | poker     | snooker | backgammon |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation | drama       | crime    |
| Hobby   | camping   | baking | photography    | skydiving |

