.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, backgammon, monopoly
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, daffodil, zinnia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, soccer, water-polo
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Game          | backgammon        | monopoly   | scrabble  | bridge   |
| Flower   | dahlia         | zinnia     | rose    | daffodil       |
| Sport         | skateboarding | lacrosse | soccer | water-polo |

