.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, airplane, helicopter
There are 4 different nationalities: american, nigerian, german, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, turtle
1. the person driving the helicopter is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the nigerian##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the german is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the american is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport   | skateboard    | airplane | helicopter | taxi        |
| Nationality       | pakistani | american  | nigerian | german     |
| Pet        | mouse    | rabbit   | turtle  | chinchilla |

