.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, hamster, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, lavender, chestnut, yellow
1. the person who likes lilac is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who likes chestnut##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Pet         | turtle  | bird | fish  | hamster |
| Sport       | volleyball | rugby        | weightlifting | cricket       |
| Color   | lilac   | lavender          | yellow          | chestnut       |

