The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary, mystery
4 different pets are kept: fish, snake, hamster, cat
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the hamster##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage         | 7up   | hot-chocolate   | sprite | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure | disaster   | mystery |
| Pet   | cat     | fish  | hamster  | snake  |

