1. the australian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Nationality         | russian | australian    | egyptian        | german |
| Pet   | mouse     | chinchilla     | goldfish        | lizard   |
| Sport         | sailing   | lacrosse | skateboarding | skiing  |

