.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
House: townhouse, victorian, colonial, farmhouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, motorbike, roller
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
8. the victorian house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta   | almond-milk  | iced-tea    | hot-chocolate    |
| House   | farmhouse | colonial  | townhouse  | victorian |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter | motorbike | car        |

