.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, tea, water
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, mah-jongg, bridge
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, hamster, frog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
5. the person playing bridge is the person drinking water##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
7. the person drinking coffee is the person playing backgammon##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee        | water    | iced-tea | tea      |
| Game   | backgammon        | bridge   | scrabble  | mah-jongg  |
| Pet         | frog | chinchilla | hamster   | hedgehog |

