.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, funk, metal, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, rowing, tennis
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, peas, papaya, cranberry
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
3. the person eating peas is on the right of the fan of blues##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | funk | metal | trance |
| Sport         | cycling | basketball | tennis  | rowing  |
| Food     | pineapple  | peas | cranberry     | papaya  |

