.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, swisher, davidoff, pall-mall
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, chef, lawyer, nurse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, punk, house, reggae
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the right of the nurse##1
3. the lawyer is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the chef##1
5. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
6. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the accountant##1
7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Cigar       | bongani | swisher | pall-mall | davidoff |
| Job         | accountant | chef  | nurse   | lawyer      |
| Music-Genre   | punk        | house  | reggae   | r&b         |

