.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, western, adventure, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, pakistani, russian
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, green, lavender, brown
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the indonesian is the person who likes lavender##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Movie-Genre           | western  | adventure  | documentary | satire |
| Nationality   | russian   | indonesian | nigerian   | pakistani      |
| Color         | aquamarine | lavender    | green   | brown         |

 